{
  "name": "tinewarm",
  "description": "A soft Rhodes electric piano glowing mellow and lo-fi cozy, tines humming in lamplight. Warm Rhodes tine-keys with a soft bell-like attack and a mellow body, a gentle lo-fi haze laid over everything — plush and intimate, warm and bright-mellow, smiling and tender. A round low tine grounds the floor; a singing mid tine-key carries the cozy melody with gentle tremolo while a brighter higher key answers; a soft creamy tone fills the plush middle; a high bell-tine chime pings with soft shimmer; tiny tine-flicks glint through the haze; a Rhodes-pad bloom swells lush and warm; a soft cloud of detuned tines shimmers; a faint tape-warm amp hum hums underneath; and a bright little tine-flick lands the tender accents. A major pentatonic @ A=432, additive and clean, never dreary — every register covered, cozy electric-piano warmth from floor to glint.",
